outputs.output_descr: The main objective of this project is to institutionalize the provision of employment support services into the Ministry of Higher Education and Scientific Research and Jordanian universities. The project will carry out a systematic approach to assess the gaps in skills and knowledge acquired by graduates of universities on one hand, and present and future trends in labor market demands on the other. The project will establish a unit within the MoHESR in order to institutionalize the provision of Employment Support services for university students and continue the assessment process.

project_descr: Institutionalize the provision of employment support services into the Ministry of Higher Education and Scientific Research and Jordanian universities.
project_title: Assesment of Education & Labor Market Gaps
